IN AFRICA, THE COMPANY IS ENGAGED IN UPSTREAM ACTIVITIES IN ANGOLA, DEMOCRATIC REPUBLIC OF THE CONGO, LIBERIA, MOROCCO, NIGERIA AND REPUBLIC OF CONGO. NET OIL-EQUIVALENT PRODUCTION AVERAGED 389

