THE COMPANY RECORDS ASSET RETIREMENT OBLIGATIONS WHEN THERE IS A LEGAL OBLIGATION ASSOCIATED WITH THE RETIREMENT OF LONG-LIVED ASSETS AND THE LIABILITY CAN BE REASONABLY ESTIMATED. THESE ASSET RETIREMENT OBLIGATIONS INCLUDE COSTS RELATED TO ENVIRONMENTAL ISSUES. THE LIABILITY BALANCE OF APPROXIMATELY

