AT

DECEMBER 31, 2016

, THE COMPANY CLASSIFIED

$4,119

OF NET PROPERTIES, PLANT AND EQUIPMENT AS “ASSETS HELD FOR SALE” ON THE CONSOLIDATED BALANCE SHEET. THESE ASSETS ARE ASSOCIATED WITH UPSTREAM OPERATIONS THAT ARE ANTICIPATED TO BE SOLD IN THE NEXT 12 MONTHS. THE REVENUES AND EARNINGS CONTRIBUTIONS OF THESE ASSETS IN 2016 WERE NOT MATERIAL.

